---
import Link from "../Link.astro";
---

<section
  id="research"
  aria-labelledby="research-heading"
  class="bg-tierra-sand px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <h2
      id="research-heading"
      class="text-center text-2xl tracking-tight sm:text-3xl"
    >
      Research-Led Conviction
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-graphite/90 sm:text-lg">
      Our strategy is informed by continuous research into regional macro
      trends, education-anchored development models, governance frameworks, and
      long-term community economics.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-graphite/90 sm:text-lg">
      We publish select insights to foster transparency, invite informed
      dialogue, and support disciplined decision-making over time.
    </p>
    <ul
      class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl list-none space-y-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-tierra-forest-dark sm:text-lg"
      role="list"
    >
      <li>
        <Link
          href="/research/why-education-anchors-community-value"
          class="text-tierra-forest underline decoration-tierra-stone underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-tierra-forest focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tierra-lime focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          Why Education Anchors Long-Term Community Value
        </Link>
      </li>
      <li>
        <Link
          href="/research"
          class="text-tierra-forest underline decoration-tierra-stone underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-tierra-forest focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tierra-lime focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          Dominican Republic: Demographics, Diaspora, and Demand
        </Link>
      </li>
      <li>
        <Link
          href="/research"
          class="text-tierra-forest underline decoration-tierra-stone underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-tierra-forest focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tierra-lime focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          Responsible Development and Long-Term Asset Performance
        </Link>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-10 text-center">
      <Link
        href="/research"
        class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-tierra-forest underline decoration-tierra-mid underline-offset-4 transition hover:decoration-tierra-forest focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tierra-lime focus:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Explore Research &amp; Insights
      </Link>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
